  "title": "L2 English Preschool Teacher - East Coast",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Plan and deliver English composition writing and language lessons in alignment with the school's guidelines and framework to achieve the desired learning outcomes.</li>\n  <li>Design and implement engaging programs and activities for children.</li>\n  <li>Create a nurturing and secure environment that fosters learning and growth.</li>\n  <li>Observe, track, and record children’s progress and development.</li>\n  <li>Organize a stimulating learning space that encourages curiosity and exploration.</li>\n  <li>Regularly update parents on their child’s progress and well-being.</li>\n  <li>Maintain continuous records of children's learning to provide regular updates to parents, along with preparing developmental portfolios and progress reports.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate closely with fellow educators, offering support and teamwork when needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/Degree in Early Childhood Care &amp; Education</li>\n  <li>L2 LON Certified by ECDA</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
